  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育平台设计一个核心数据流架构。主要围绕学生数据库、内容分发网络和课堂服务这三个核心组件展开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个核心组件。我先把StudentDB作为起点，然后它需要连接到ContentCDN来分发学习资料，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，StudentDB是源头，学生信息要先进入CDN体系。另外CDN还要直接支撑ClassroomService的实时课堂功能。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画出了StudentDB到CDN，以及CDN到ClassroomService的连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "CDN内部其实还有一层逻辑，需要区分静态内容分发和动态内容回源，所以ContentCDN应该再细分出一个子节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是说从主CDN再分出一个ContentCDN子节点？那这两个CDN节点之间是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，主CDN负责调度，子CDN负责具体的内容交付。同时主CDN还需要有一条回源链路回到StudentDB做数据同步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：主CDN分出子CDN节点，同时主CDN回连到StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "现在ClassroomService需要回写数据到StudentDB，课堂中的互动记录要持久化。同时子CDN也需要回源到StudentDB获取个性化内容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "添加了两条回源线：ClassroomService到StudentDB，以及子CDN到StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "子CDN还有一个重要链路，它需要连接到GradeSync服务，成绩相关的敏感数据要走专门的同步通道。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "GradeSync是一个独立服务？它接收子CDN的数据，然后流向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
