      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，ClassroomService需要双路数据：一路是实时课堂数据，一路是持久化后的学生档案。下游StudentDB同时给ClassroomService和CDN提供查询服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
