      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ClassroomService内部也需要扩展，主服务要分出子服务节点，专门处理课堂内的多媒体流。这个子ClassroomService要回连到CDN获取资源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：主ClassroomService分出子节点，子ClassroomService连接到CDN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我看一下图。GradeSync那边是不是也应该连到CDN？成绩数据的静态报表需要CDN分发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "目前GradeSync只连了ClassroomService，没有到CDN的链路。需要补上吗？",
