      "utterance": "添加GradeSync到CDN的连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 25,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "CDN这边我再确认下，现在有两个CDN节点了，它们之间需要直接通信吗？比如主CDN到子CDN的内容预热？",
      "elements_involved": [
